{"tid":1925153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡耀昌向平機會投訴食店不招待內地客 民主黨「割席」50黨員聯署促辭中委","createTime":"2020-03-14T07:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T08:57:52.000Z","uid":105567,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e27a21be7e0a23be1197b434b60d274ceb4ccbaa","tid":1925153,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:23:43.000Z","msg":"身兼民主黨中委的社區組織協會幹事蔡耀昌，日前向平機會投訴食肆不招待內地人屬「歧視」，又促請港府修例禁歧視內地人或新移民。其言論一出令民主黨亦遭牽連，繼民主黨昨晚發聲明與蔡劃清界線後，多名民主黨成員聯署中委會，促請蔡辭任中委。民主黨主席胡志偉稱，中委會今午會召開特別會議聽取黨員意見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200314/NGGFDBMG6EUYMR6AZW77MEA4K4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200314%2FNGGFDBMG6EUYMR6AZW77MEA4K4%2F&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCQexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=fc06d0cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200314%2FNGGFDBMG6EUYMR6AZW77MEA4K4%2F&h=70abd361\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200314/NGGFDBMG6EUYMR6AZW77MEA4K4/</a>"},{"pid":"b834865b0c7a79266fdb0d78b244f372acacf707","tid":1925153,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:26:02.000Z","msg":"唔該聽埋民意，踢走隻共諜"},{"pid":"23c050ac2d8d6f2241fefa8afcc727617f134790","tid":1925153,"uid":126731,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T08:57:52.000Z","msg":"共狗蔡耀昌終於現形"}]}